PRO TIPS FOR SUMMER HAIR CARE WITH MELROY FROM MATRIX
During the summer season, the warm breeze, can cause harm to our hair. The extreme heat, direct sunlight, warm breeze with mositure can cause severe damage right from the start of the summer. Instead of resorting to a quick trim or a haircut, you can instead use the right hair care products, follow a home care routine that will suit your hair for the summer and for all the seasons to come.
